<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM9.7">
<l>iṉṟuvan tittaṉai yumamu tucey tiṭappeṟilnā</l>
<l>ṉoṉṟunū ṟāyi ramākkoṭut tuppiṉ ṉumāḷumceyvaṉ</l>
<l>teṉṟal maṇaṅka maḻuntiru māliruñ cōlaitaṉṉuḷ</l>
<l>niṉṟa pirāṉaṭi yēṉmaṉat tēvantu nērpaṭilē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If [I] get the Lord who has stood in Tirumāliruñcōlai,</l>
<l rend="indent">where the southern breeze emits fragrance,</l>
<l>to come today and eat all these,</l>
<l>If [He] comes and appears in [my] heart—[of me,] a slave,</l>
<l>I will give a hundred thousand [pots] for each [that I pledged];</l>
<l rend="indent">And then, I will also serve [Him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
